--| Object Name    : XX_INV_ITEM_MASTER_ATTRIBUTES and XX_INV_ITEM_ORG_ATTRIBUTES for  Items     |--                       
--|                                                                                              |--
--| Program Name   : XX_INV_ITEM_MASTER_ORG.tbl                                                  |--        
--|                                                                                              |--   
--| Purpose        : Alter the  Tables in LINK instance .                                        |--
--|                  The Objects to be altered  are:                                             |--
--|                                                                                              |--
--|                  1.XX_INV_ITEM_MASTER_ATTRIBUTES            |--
--|                  2.XX_INV_ITEM_ORG_ATTRIBUTES                                                |--                                                                                               
